Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:41.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:51.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:59.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:06.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:13.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:17.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:27.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:34.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:40.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:52.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:59.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:41.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能讓你忘卻傷痛 我寧願捨棄笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.15,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言語的她 默然低下了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:51.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任憑淚水洗刷著夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:59.66,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延著凍結一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:06.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛這無可喘息的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:13.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:17.00,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被這可悲的理由束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.97,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:27.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}淚水的彼岸 那閃耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:34.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狹小的窗口中 滿眼是往昔的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:40.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然無法像鳥兒一樣飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:52.47,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為讓悲傷永遠銘記於心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:59.76,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了忘卻而閉目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:41.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:46.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:57.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷つけあうの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:03.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:07.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:16.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また会えると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:27.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:33.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:38.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:51.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だったら信じあえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:56.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:41.79,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}猶如花朵隨風起舞 猶如雨水滋潤大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:46.16,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}這個世界如此緊密不分 如此活潑生機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:57.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}卻為何人們互相傷害 為何離別突然降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:03.36,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遙遠的地方 你總會留在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:07.68,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份溫柔的笑顏依舊映在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:16.84,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}擁抱著你的碎片 刺痛著我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.62,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}心心連系 要相信一定會再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:22.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:27.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:33.33,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}想要分擔你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:38.63,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:44.20,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無論身處黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:51.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:56.71,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠不再分離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙就是所謂「物質」了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便出手了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:47.80,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}お金があっても　友達は買えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:59.73,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}なにもなくてもね　みんながいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:05.02,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}みんな聞いて　僕たちの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.70,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}みんな知って　僕たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:15.90,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}あなたはどうしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.73,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}僕はね　元気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:27.09,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}あなたはどうしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:33.33,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}僕はね　元気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:47.80,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}即使有錢 也不能買到友情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:59.73,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}即使一無所有 還有大家陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:05.02,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}請大家傾聽我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.70,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}讓大家了解我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:15.90,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}你會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.73,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}我很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:27.09,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}你會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:33.33,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}我很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 詩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這首歌是 瑪麗娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了!? 為什麼能聽到歌聲!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我要…戰斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到布林格竟然走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的話 我來安慰你也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在怒火中燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格·斯塔維迪這窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然打倒了變革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞·愛德好像選則了和我們敵對的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這是很美妙的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常美妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有MS正在接近?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個Gundam是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位去把醫務兵叫來!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 振作一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那… 剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器和光學攝像機都沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片空域應該沒有聯邦軍布防
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去匯合點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的補給部隊好像已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對給我們提供情報的KATARON說聲謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會轉達的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先把能修的地方修好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝協助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 Seraphim也用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 就要被變革者的機體打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們注意到Seraphim的特性了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先接受KATARON的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從聯邦的包圍網中逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現如今 托勒密的火器管制不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果A-LAWS攻過來 馬上就會垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是00 Raiser的話 應該能打開局面的 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達匯合點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政變的主謀就是你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦議會無視輿論 創立了獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且擴大軍力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至決心使用衛星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種所作所為 無法坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看A-LAWS哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有小看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是A-LAWS 也有無法出手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要把軌道電梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想讓我加入政變?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無法違抗軍隊紀律的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的話 赫利她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來見你是希望你不要插手這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我睜一只眼閉一只眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作為軍人 而是作為老朋友的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和你交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈切裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞魯哥 我曾經說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊是為了守護國民和國家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而存在的對外勢力的抑制力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 錯誤的政治下 軍隊不會擁有正確的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所希望的 是在正確的軍隊中作為軍人生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 你們不會把政變開始的時間地點告訴KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了防止情報洩漏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望KATARON看過我們的奮斗後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出是否協助我們的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要前期的幫助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請全部交由我們這邊來做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓各支部知道你們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有和他們聯絡的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他們擁有可以和A-LAWS對抗的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為有邀請他們的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過了吧 我相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是為數不多的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛回到地上就要戰斗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有想過要有一點女人味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在那個叫沙慈的人面前?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經拋棄過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你應該把復仇心也捨棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛手段的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給本大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 無視我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我們這樣可以互通心思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來裡傑諾是不會參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那孩子變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官大人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 作為人類還可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候您多時了 瑪奈金大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隸屬MS開發部的比利·片桐技術大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到本艦打擾一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術部門的為什麼要到現場來?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想親眼見證天行者的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也獲得了司令的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個願望馬上就能實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有這種程度的戰力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要小動作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們做個了斷吧 久篠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS擁有的戰力差不多可以輕松毀滅天行者了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很抱歉 不過就讓我利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軀體獻給神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔赴這場聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被神明承認 被神明寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化身為神的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前你都跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守護神明的教誨才!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上並沒有神明!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只會孕生出暴力的卑劣的儀式!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把這家伙從家裡放出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛… 洛克昂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的東西裡能夠改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你現在的心情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他什麼都改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,譬如別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況是生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:12:01.14,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}失くす事が拾うためなら　別れるのは出会うため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:12.19,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}さよならのあとにはきっとこんにちはと出会うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:23.56,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs40}緑色芝生に寝転んでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:12:01.14,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}若失去是為了重獲 那麼分別既是為了重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:12.19,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}再見之後一定能再言你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:23.56,INcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}躺在綠瑩瑩的草地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替沒能改變的我……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜… 這裡是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷已經好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽到的那首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用這些孩子的願望寫成的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在TRANS-AM中聽到了那首歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然彈頭已經取出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡沒有細胞活性裝置什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是讓傷口痊愈這段時間也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前 你給我的信裡這麼寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人相互理解的方法是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在尋找著那個答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須從相互了解開始的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就留一些 相互了解的時間也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 要戰斗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正在做著准備喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會回來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 那要看時運如何吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼正經地回答啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險 回房間裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人正在甜甜蜜蜜中哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯戰爭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然有那樣的過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是十多年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎惡戰爭的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在一個隨處可見的普通家庭裡被養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話 原本想走上那條道路的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我血統的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才被選為阿扎帝斯坦的王女…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起當一國的王女來說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來更適合演奏音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我一直在勉強自己吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來也是同樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己而戰斗著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報說你的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歐洲支部接受了補給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了KATARON籌措的補給物資
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外壁部分的修整馬上就可以完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人打過來之前 看來能派上用場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是潛水模式還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器火控系統也還有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行作業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能迷上我的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍MS隊 向本艦接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由粒子放出量判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測敵軍部隊為A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人完全掌握了這邊的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 敵人的數量是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機總數36架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有36架!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎新型機MA也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來全力而戰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 順序出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密將山脈作為護盾回避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不讓我上MS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下你不是被稱作不死身麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我沾沾光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦已經負傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加蒂莎 用Enplus拖住Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的機體專心攻擊敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此一戰要和那些家伙作個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射程竟然超過了加蒂莎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用先制攻擊減少敵人數量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 別省著粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解! 了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈無虛發!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種粒子束的威力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用TRANS-AM系統的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體 散開!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的攻擊有臨界時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前不要隨便接近!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 挺有一手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨界時間 到達! 臨界時間 到達!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再裝填完成之前靠你們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 提艾利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓敵人接近托勒密!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM結束了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體 開始突擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一口氣攻向敵艦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 Gundam來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們喲!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打開反擊的突破口…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 敵人來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 裝填中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 裝填中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍部隊 接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離射擊距離 還有0034!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝無法使用!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有GN Archer的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架MS是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的… 機體?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身體沒問題麼? 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰友們在等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我聽聽孩子們的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你也要平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾 出擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手 露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久篠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣天行者也就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部傳來的緊急加密通信?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍動向有變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:51.07,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子炮束攻擊停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.99,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍部隊 全體轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.93,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開現空域…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人撤掉了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政… 政變…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道電梯竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被占領了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON傳來的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲塔附近發生政變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍進行了包圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 托勒密也會向那裡去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Flag吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信知道了非洲塔這邊發生的事情後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就肯定能遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退開!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間跟你耗著…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被這麼冷淡地甩了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定要讓你只看著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由盟友制造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾愛機「豪傑」的奧義!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著政變派占領的軌道電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方部隊如被引領一般集結而來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 邁向悲劇的序章
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對人類的肅清 即將開始



